-^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^
-
-``LAPACK_FOUND``
-  Lapack libraries were found
-``LAPACK_<component>_FOUND``
-  LAPACK <component> specified was found
-``LAPACK_LIBRARIES``
-  Lapack library files (including BLAS
